replyContent:
The sight words at this app are based on Dolch list, which is the most commonly used set of sight words. You can select which sight words should be used at the App Settings, please check it. 
The app is designed for landscape use. Please contact our technical support and we'll be happy to help you.

replyContent: If you use the same account, you should be able to reinstall the app for free (as any other app on Google Play). Please check your receipts if you were really charged. Unfortunately, there is nothing we can do with similar issues, we are just an app developer, we have no control over the store. Please contact Google Play customer support for a help
